{"tid":1950194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"侵侵想到紐約探訪野戰醫院 特勤局直接拒絕","createTime":"2020-03-30T07:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T08:25:24.000Z","uid":25468,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d62eca5dbc41760df1be522addddfa07ba6c5cb9","tid":1950194,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/30/phpyNTw3F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F30%2FphpyNTw3F.jpg&h=9bb37dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普表示，他原本打算去紐約市探訪明天開放的賈維茨中心（Javits Center）野戰醫院，但特勤局拒絕讓他前往。<br />\n<br />\n據《CNN》報導，川普在武漢肺炎簡報會透露，由賈維茨中心改建的醫院明天啟用，「我非常想去那裡，但特勤局和相關人員都不允許我這樣做」，川普隨後還再度強調，「出於明顯的原因，他們不會讓我去」。<br />\n<br />\n川普指出，賈維茨中心野戰醫院共有2900張病床，而且是由聯邦政府改建而成，並非是紐約州政府出力。川普說，美國陸軍工兵團也參與了這項工程。<br />\n<br />\n美國特勤局發言人對此表示，出於安全的考量，特勤局不會討論受保護者、保護手段、保護方法和相關任務的內容。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/30/phpyImM2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F30%2FphpyImM2e.jpg&h=a35f82ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/30/phpjZ3HFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F30%2FphpjZ3HFX.jpg&h=ae729ee4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b2f8c586bda3a3ee8ddf74637d083def4f74c80","tid":1950194,"uid":35456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9e536eeafd48bcc7f1aeeaa181aa7f9a92c7965","tid":1950194,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"（粉嶺要人！急！）今日下午有大量還押手足上庭跪求聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949806</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c292e7613c9d09fd65828f173d55dbd605a13af3","ti